ORDER
The defendant’s motion for limited remand or in the alternative for reduction of bail is assigned to the motion calendar for June 20, 1980 at 9:30 a. m. for oral argument.
WEISBERGER, J., did not participate.

attorneys: Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., for plaintiff.
Mary E. Levesque, Asst. Public Defender, for defendant.
casebody.head_matter:
STATE v. Richard A. FRAZIER.
No. 78-442-C.A.
Supreme Court of Rhode Island.
June 12, 1980.
Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., for plaintiff.
Mary E. Levesque, Asst. Public Defender, for defendant.
